column5: Really truley  sorry for getting all excited about ice fishing again. Since I got the hut and lic,it,s been mild and raining. It,s all my fault.Nice start to the new year. LOL   Maybe next weekend.
Frost even came out of the ground.. I think it's a sign !!!
thanks alot.... i finished work wednesday dec 22nd, and was deathly sick till dec 28th, and now its raining and i cant fish. lol
There's still ice out there, just gotta find it
